.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
ibaddr [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
Display the lid (and range) as well as the GID address of the
port specified (by DR path, lid, or GUID) or the local port by default.
.sp
Note: this utility can be used as simple address resolver.
